snippet.textDisplay: I wish I had such a supportive family. I cannot understand the grief in all of them. Every. Single. One. Of them. And they are obviously not inauthentic! I can't imagine this kind of bond with anyone. I've learnt to act like leaving is such a light topic that now I don't even have any particular emotional reaction to this video. Maybe I feel angry. Because I didn't have such a family and that I don't have this kind of support. I don't have anyone to trust. I have no one to turn to. They do. Not hating here. I just feel so lonely, so here my little rant goes. And I truly admire their relationship. Peace and love \/
